         <div type="translation">
            <ab>OIM 19383, recto: (1) Amenothes son of Psenamounis, 1/6 (silver kite), and Taminis his mother, 1/6 silver (kite), (2) makes 1/3 silver (kite) for the price of oil of Phaophi, (3) has written Esminis (on) Egyptian year 38, Phaophi 28.</ab>
